title: SwifTEA: Major Hints ‘1989' Re-Recording Is Next
description:
Did you catch all of those Easter eggs in Taylor Swift's interview with Stephen Colbert? There were A LOT and she continues to blow our mind! Nick, Amy, Lacey and Ana try to uncover all of the clues but one thing is for sure.. We know what she is re-recording next!
What did we miss? Hit us up with any of your thoughts, Swifties! There are a lot of ways to reach us!
